===''Year Zero''===
[[Image:yearzero cover323.jpg|thumb|200px|[[Year Zero (album)|Year Zero]]<br />(2007)]]
{{main|Year Zero (album)}}
The upcoming Nine Inch Nails studio album is ''[[Year Zero (album)|Year Zero]]'', to be released on [[April 17]], [[2007]].<ref>{{cite web
| url = http://www.nin.com/current/index.html
| title = nine inch nails: current
| date = [[2007-02-05]]
| publisher = NIN.com
| accessdate = 2007-02-05
}}</ref>
The first single, entitled "[[Survivalism (Nine Inch Nails song)|Survivalism]]," was due for radio airplay on [[March 6]]<ref>{{cite web
| url = http://www.fmqb.com/Article.asp?id=350363
| title = Quick Hits: Nine Inch Nails, John Legend, Metallica, The Shins, The Arcade Fire, Rufus Wainwright, Flaming Lips, The View
| publisher = FMQB
| date = [[2007-02-13]]
