}}</ref> but received its worldwide premiere on [[February 16]] on [[95.5 WBRU]] (WBRU-FM, Providence) due to the record label moving up the release date of the single after a separate single, "My Violent Heart", was leaked out on to the Internet. Other stations are currently playing "[[Survivalism (Nine Inch Nails song)|Survivalism]]," <ref>{{cite web
| url = http://www.fmqb.com/Article.asp?id=350363
| title = Quick Hits: Nine Inch Nails, John Legend, Metallica, The Shins, The Arcade Fire, Rufus Wainwright, Flaming Lips, The View
