}}</ref>

On February 27, [[Side-Line]] magazine announced that the UK band [[Ladytron]] were to go on tour with NIN in Europe after Trent presonally invited them<ref>[http://www.side-line.com/news_comments.php?id=21088_0_2_0_C Ladytron goes on tour with NIN]</ref>. 
